Package: iNZightUpdate
Title: An updater for the iNZight desktop apps
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Elliott", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "tom.elliott@auckland.ac.nz")
    )
Description: The iNZightVIT desktop apps require updating,
    so this package allows us to control that process
    as a simple R project (which can itself be updated).
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Suggests: tcltk
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
